<li>have shown that overexpression of Rob ( or its N-terminal domain alone ) activates transcription of sodA ( encoding man-ganese-containing superoxide dismutase ) , fumC ( encoding fumarase C ) , inaA ( encoding a weak acid-inducible protein ) , and micF ( gene for an antisense RNA repressing the outer membrane porin OmpF ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=10850996" target="_blank">10850996</a>]<br></li>
